Works from time to time

```bash
keywindid=''
for id in `xdotool search --class 'VirtualBox'`
do 
  if xprop -id $id | grep '_NET_WM_NAME.*epam2.*1"$' > /dev/null
  then 
    keywinid=$id
  fi 
done

